Comprehensive Service Provider in Man-machine Interaction and Wireless Communication Technology, Striving to Fulfill Its Missions

Founded in 2006, ITON (stock code: 830982) is a national innovative high-tech enterprise and a "Specialized, Fined, Differential and Innovative Enterprise” in Guangdong. It was listed on the NEEQ market in 2014.  We're committed  to providing customers with the R&D and production of products based on Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, Zigbee, Sub-1G, 4G, 5G and other wireless communication and perception fusion technologies. 

We also provide customers with comprehensive technical services and product ODM services for wireless communication/data transmission modules, functional products based on human-computer interaction, IoT/AIoT functional products and integrated solutions. 

Make every intelligent product equipped with ITON's intelligent hardware control and processing module.
