Our company offers a wide range of services in the field of product conformity assessment to the requirements of the National Conformity Assessment System of the Republic of Belarus:
- Technical Regulations of the Republic of Belarus "Telecommunication facilities. Security" TR 024BY (means of radio and wired communication);
- Energy efficiency of household appliances, as well as access to the Eurasian Economic Union (EAEU) market - Belarus, Russia, Kazakhstan, Armenia, Kyrgyzstan in terms of assessing compliance with the requirements of the Technical Regulations of the Eurasian Economic Union (TR EAC):
- TR CU 004/2011 (On safety of low-voltage equipment);
- TR CU 010/2011 (On safety of machinery and equipment);
- TR CU 016/2011 (On safety of devices operating on gaseous fuel);
- TR CU 020/2011 (Electromagnetic compatibility of technical equipment);
- TR CU 032/2013 (On the safety of excess pressure equipment);
- EAEU TR 037/2016 (On restriction of using hazardous substances in the electrical and radioelectronic articles). 
- provision of services of a person authorized by the manufacturer to perform actions on his behalf when confirming conformity and placing products on the single customs territory of the Eurasian Economic Union (national representative) in accordance with the requirements of legislation in the field of technical regulation of the Republic of Belarus and the Eurasian Economic Union;
Advantages of our company are: 
- our employees have the highest qualifications and more than 10 years of experience in the system of conformity assessment, development of standards, technical requirements, quality management systems, etc.;
- our company does not require prepayment for the performance of work in terms of conformity assessment, payment is made upon completion of work; 
- for our regular customers, work in terms of consulting on the requirements of standards, technical regulations and other regulatory and technical documents is provided free of charge.

Based on 5G, we are offering 5G related devices including:

1. Telecom/ISP market: 5G CPE and WiFi6 Router;
2. SMB Market: 5G Router and Gateway;
3. Industry Market: Industrial 5G Router.

Located in Wuhan, China, we own the first class R&D Team and world-class supply chain on manufacturing. It has capability of making 9M pieces products per month.

Our vision is that we believe "wireless connects a better life".

