We accept orders for the design pcb antennas and antenna arrays in the range up to 40 GHz based on Rogers, Arlon and FR-4 materials.

- design of pcb antennas taking into account the placement, housing, layout of the device;
- design of pcb antennas with a radiation pattern of a required width and shape;
- design of broadband antennas and antenna arrays with high gain;
assembling, soldering, measurements.

To get the result, we only need the technical specification and the design of the device. We will select the type of antenna, make an electrodynamic calculation with minimizing the VSWR and make a gerber file for production. After manufacturing the pcb, we will measure the characteristics and send the final gerber to the customer.

Mobility & Wireless Solutions Inc. (MWSI) is a Management Consulting, Project Management and Service Development Company that creates new wireless service solutions for Government and Industry. Clients include Innovation, Science & Economic Development Canada (ISED), Global Affairs Canada, National Defence and the Ottawa International Airport among others.  Specific Technical/Operational Expertise includes:

  - Next Generation 5G, IOT, Cloud and AI (Artificial Intelligence) Strategy;
  - Wireless Public Alerting;
  - Broadband Wireless (Microwave IP Radio);
  - Enterprise Wireless LAN (Wi-Fi)
  - In-Building Cellular Distributed Antenna Systems (DAS)
  - Wireless Intrusion Prevention Systems (WIPS)

MWSI employs PMP/PMBOK Disciplines to ensure the technology itself doesn't distract everyone from the overarching business objectives, functional expectations, etc.  A key competency for MWSI is the development of comprehensive requirements at the business, policy, operational, functional and technical levels.  This forms the baseline through which projects are delivered on schedule, on budget and within scope.

MWSI is also very flexible.  We can lead the team or be part of the team. We can work at the technical, operational and/or policy levels. Sometimes, we simply provide advice as a Management Consultants. Let us know how we can help you.  You can reach our Principal Consultant (Tyler Cashion) at Tyler.Cashion@MobilityandWireless.ca or (613) 404-3517 for both voice or text message.

